<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Vasilis — data scientist, ML engineer, and lifelong learner.">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-4xl">
    About
  </h1>

  <div class="mt-8 prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Vasilis. I'm a data scientist and machine learning engineer with a passion for
      turning complex data into actionable insights and building intelligent systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      My work spans the full ML lifecycle — from exploratory data analysis and feature
      engineering to model training, evaluation, and deployment. I enjoy working with
      Python and its rich ecosystem of tools for data science and machine learning.
    </p>

    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Data Science & ML</strong> — Statistical modeling, deep learning, NLP, and
        building end-to-end ML pipelines</li>
      <li><strong>Software Engineering</strong> — Writing clean, maintainable code and building
        tools that make data work easier</li>
      <li><strong>Philosophy</strong> — Epistemology, philosophy of science, and the
        philosophical foundations of probability and statistics</li>
      <li><strong>Cats</strong> — Proud cat person. Check out the <a href="/cats/">cat gallery</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>About This Site</h2>
    <p>
      This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a>
      and <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tailwind CSS</a>,
      and hosted on GitHub Pages. All content is written in Markdown/MDX and version-controlled with Git.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
